data.name: Pumped Up Kicks by Foster The People
data.description: Released in 2010 as their debut single, "Pumped Up Kicks" slingshot Foster The People into the No. 3 spot on the Billborad Hot 100 for eight consecutive weeks, and on top op that received a Grammy Award Nomination for Best Pop Duo/Group Performance. Check out the lyric by lyric account of Foster the People’s haunting hit song with songwriter/frontman Mark Foster.

data.name: Feel It Still by Portugal. The Man
data.description: Just released in the spring of 2017, "Feel It Still" quickly became one of the biggest chart cross-overs of the 2010s, hitting No. 1 on the US Alternative Charts and peaking at No. 4 on the Billboard Hot 100 by fall of the same year. Check out the in-depth commentary with Portugal. The Man on their magnetic single "Feel It Still."
